# Case overview KPI semantics

The **seven** tiles at the top of **case Summary** (`CaseOverviewSummaryCards.svelte`) define the **canonical** accent color (`ds-occ-kpi-card--*`) and **Heroicon outline** per domain.

**Full table:** [docs/CASE_OVERVIEW_KPI_CANON.md](docs/CASE_OVERVIEW_KPI_CANON.md)

**Rule:** When styling sections, nav items, or list rows for **timeline, notes, files, entities, workflow, proposals, or warrants**, align with that row’s **CSS variant + icon** — do not introduce alternate palette slots for the same domain without an explicit design ticket.
